                            <comment id="17463757" author="martijnvisser" created="Wed, 22 Dec 2021 11:48:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=yang-y&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;yang-y&quot;&gt;yang-y&lt;/a&gt; Please change the contents of this ticket to English&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17463766" author="ana4" created="Wed, 22 Dec 2021 12:03:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;cc &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=dianfu&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;dianfu&quot;&gt;dianfu&lt;/a&gt; I want to fix this.&#160; I will add the &apos;--no-index&apos; option in PythonEnvironmentManagerUtils#pipInstallRequirements method, when the requirementsCacheDir is not null.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When we set &apos;--no-index&apos;, it will only install with offline, never download from the internet.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When we do not set &apos;--no-index&apos;, it will first download from the internet, and then install with offline.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
